{"tid":1065242,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A]《Another Eden：超越時空的貓》(8)","createTime":"2019-03-17T06:23:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T07:52:01.000Z","uid":22465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7dc467d5c2ea7fc77e13d58e317f7c37abe3d2a8","tid":1065242,"uid":22465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T06:23:13.000Z","msg":"誤中1001<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nGoogle Play：<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=games.wfs.anothereden\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dgames.wfs.anothereden&d=vfAPSPM9tzlrjOAF5hGH%2FwUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=16d6f3f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=games.wfs.anothereden</a><br />\n<br />\nApp Store：<br />\n<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/app/id1439565347\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fapp%2Fid1439565347&d=vfAPSPM9tzlrjOAF5hGH%2FwUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=95fd6f21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/app/id1439565347</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ.建唔建議首抽?<br />\nA.唔建議,因為刷一次首抽要差唔多30分鐘,要5星奶開局不如8591/淘寶<br />\n<br />\nQ.首抽抽咩好<br />\nA.5星奶-瑪莉(大獎)&gt;其次土法(杜娃)水法(麥提)<br />\n<br />\nQ.有冇得同人玩?<br />\nA.冇,只係一隻單機到GAME,抽到5星唔洗拎上黎曬,冇人想知<br />\n<br />\nQ.副本係咩黎?<br />\nA.係副本可以打到角色既職業書,升星書<br />\n每日0200、0800、1400、2000時會回復1次。<br />\n打完第11章,係次元就會開放HARD難度<br />\n打完第25章,係次元就會開放VERY HARD難度<br />\n<br />\n副本與角色升星<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=29220&amp;snA=770&amp;tnum=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D29220%26snA%3D770%26tnum%3D2&d=vfAPSPM9tzlrjOAF5hGH%2FwUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=aa0b5363\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=29220&amp;snA=770&amp;tnum=2</a><br />\n<br />\nQ.爆左機之後有咩做<br />\nA.現階段國際版v1.1,岩岩更新左外傳,可以刷下魔力,之後都係副本刷料做武器,儲下圖鑑<br />\n<br />\nQ.過左劇情,d怪打唔返點算?<br />\nA.去次元夾縫左邊度門,有得入返去打過左既劇情<br />\n<br />\nQ.主角群洗唔洗升<br />\nA.升啦,男主,大波艾美,田雞,海蕾娜,莉卡都有得上5星,係爭阿妹未有<br />\n<br />\nQ.邊到打最多經<br />\nA.現階段國際版v1.1 - 魔獸城,最常出4隻<br />\n<br />\nQ.角色能力盤點數夠唔夠用?<br />\nA.當你最高lv時,夠你點曬佢<br />\n<br />\nQ.戰鬥相關問題<br />\nA.力量-物攻<br />\n智力-魔攻,補量<br />\n耐力-物防<br />\n精神-魔防<br />\n速度-行動順序<br />\n幸運-爆擊率<br />\n<br />\nQ.有冇網站推介<br />\nA.https://<a href=\"http://games.gaym.jp/iPhone/another-eden/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgames.gaym.jp%2FiPhone%2Fanother-eden%2F&d=vfAPSPM9tzlrjOAF5hGH%2FwUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=0568278d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">games.gaym.jp/iPhone/another-eden/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://altema.jp/anaden/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faltema.jp%2Fanaden%2F&d=vfAPSPM9tzlrjOAF5hGH%2FwUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=75c94883\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://altema.jp/anaden/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/B.php?bsn=29220&amp;subbsn=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FB.php%3Fbsn%3D29220%26subbsn%3D0&d=vfAPSPM9tzlrjOAF5hGH%2FwUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=73647964\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/B.php?bsn=29220&amp;subbsn=0</a> 巴哈<br />\n<br />\nQ.仲有冇其他野要注意?<br />\nA.除左信箱每日送20石之外,買石個到仲有10石拎,總共30石"},{"pid":"d5c3dea6e1d7348fd3f0579721ebb54951299e15","tid":1065242,"uid":22465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T06:24:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Google Play：<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=games.wfs.anothereden\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dgames.wfs.anothereden&d=vfAPSPM9tzlrjOAF5hGH%2FwUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=16d6f3f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=games.wfs.anothereden</a><br />\n<br />\nApp Store：<br />\n<